    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver that balances luxury with everyday utility. On the outside, the paint retains a deep gloss and the body panels are straight, though a keen eye might spot a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with highway commuting. The alloy wheels are free of curb rash and are currently wrapped in high-quality tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin remains a quiet sanctuary; the leather upholstery is supple and shows only light softening on the driver's bolster, while the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All electronic features\u2014including the premium sound system, dual-zone climate control, and navigation\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is exceptionally sound, having followed a strict manufacturer-recommended maintenance schedule with a comprehensive service history available. It shifts smoothly, brakes firmly, and offers a confident, rattle-free ride. This is a solid, honest vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next chapter.",
